"with the <keycap>Tab</keycap> key, keyboard focus should move between "
"controls in a predictable order. In Western locales, this is normally left "
"to right and top to bottom."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: C/index.docbook:921
msgid ""
